The Glow Revolution Starts Now

Say hello to Sunehri, India’s first serum-mist hybrid designed for skin that battles the harshest summer days. Infused with floral waters, ginseng, centella, and rosehip oil, this glow-boosting mist hydrates, heals, and highlights — all in just 2–3 refreshing sprays.

Not Just a Mist. A Skin Solution.

Sunehri isn’t just a cosmetic fix — it’s a powerful skincare solution. It targets the 4Ds of skin stress:
• Dehydration: Deep hydration that lasts 24 hours with botanical waters & Vitamin E
• Damage: Repairs and calms with Centella Asiatica and Ginseng
• Dullness: Revives glow instantly with antioxidant-rich Rosehip Oil
• Dark Spots: Fades uneven tone and sun damage with regular use

Why You’ll Love It
• Glass Skin Glow: Lightweight serum-mist finish that gives a lit-from-within radiance
• Sets & Refreshes Makeup: Locks in makeup, removes cakiness, and revives your base
• Minimizes Pores & Controls Oil: Summer-proof formula keeps skin fresh, not shiny
• Multi-Tasking Marvel: Toner + Setting Spray + Hydrator + Glow Serum – in one
• Ayurvedic & Vegan: Backed by botanicals, powered by modern skin science

Who It’s For
• All skin types – dry, oily, sensitive, and combo
• People exposed to sun, pollution, screens & stress
• Anyone wanting a healthy, dewy glow without stickiness

What’s Inside the Bottle
• 120ml of golden magic
• Floral waters (Rose, Tuberose)
• Centella Asiatica
• Korean Ginseng
• Rosehip Oil + Vitamin E
• Mexican Tuberose infusion
• Non-comedogenic, non-toxic, and cruelty-free

Why SUNEHRI?
• Ayurvedic + Active ingredients
• Dermatologically tested
• Just ₹499 for a long-lasting bottle
• Made with love, in India
